txt.en: Defeated many fell path-finders in Minas Morgul.
You have defeated many fell path-finders in the Circle of Sorrow. The Rangers of Ithilien will be pleased with your efforts.

Away from the Shrouded Forge, the Dead take the path that is forced upon them. Fell path-finders follow the stream of spirits to their destination, allowing nothing to stand in their way. You should defeat these path-finders to allow the Rangers of Ithilien to move about the city with fewer worries.
Fell path-finders can be found in the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should defeat any fell path-finders that you find.
